{"meta":{"updateDate":1755117017722,"pPcc":"SAT#S","questionId":"fc8aa563","skill_cd":"S.D.","score_band_range_cd":4,"skill_desc":"Circles","createDate":1755117017722,"program":"SAT","primary_class_cd_desc":"Geometry and Trigonometry","ibn":"","external_id":"af30d73b-01f0-4546-bd51-0d5af9b64d57","primary_class_cd":"S","uId":"847326f0-04fa-4e5d-ba32-49487eeab5d6","difficulty":"M"},"source":"modern","detail":{"type":"mcq","stem":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">What is the center of the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane defined by the equation <math alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<msup>\n\t\t\t<mfenced>\n\t\t\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t\t\t\t<mo>-</mo>\n\t\t\t\t\t<mn>1</mn>\n\t\t\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t\t</mfenced>\n\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t</msup>\n\t\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t\t<msup>\n\t\t\t<mfenced>\n\t\t\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t\t\t<mi>y</mi>\n\t\t\t\t\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t\t\t\t\t<mn>7</mn>\n\t\t\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t\t</mfenced>\n\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t</msup>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>1</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>?</p>","keys":["acc09b87-ef6c-4e95-b71b-ea89618f4ac5"],"answerOptions":[{"id":"f7a4299c-5ed8-4802-b814-696f8f72d78c","content":"<p><math alttext=\"left parenthesis negative 1 comma negative 7 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>"},{"id":"8cef9a24-b3a6-40f5-b683-c7444bc9e00e","content":"<p><math alttext=\"left parenthesis negative 1 comma 7 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>"},{"id":"acc09b87-ef6c-4e95-b71b-ea89618f4ac5","content":"<p><math alttext=\"left parenthesis 1 comma negative 7 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>"},{"id":"931679fa-7b71-48ae-ac15-c1364419c206","content":"<p><math alttext=\"left parenthesis 1 comma 7 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>"}],"rationale":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is correct. The equation of a circle in the <em>x</em><em>y</em>-plane can be written as <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus h right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y minus k right parenthesis squared equals r squared\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>h</mi><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>k</mi><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, where the center of the circle is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis h comma k right parenthesis\"><mo>(</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>k</mi><mo>)</mo></math> and the radius of the circle is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"r\"><mi>r</mi></math>. It's given that the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane is defined by the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>. This equation&nbsp;can be written as <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y minus left parenthesis negative 7 right parenthesis right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>)</mo><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>. For this equation, it follows that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"h equals 1\"><mi>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"k equals negative 7\"><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn></math>. Therefore, the center of the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane defined by the given equation is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis 1 comma negative 7 right parenthesis\"><mo>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>)</mo></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is incorrect. This is the center of the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane that is defined by the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x plus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect. This is the center of the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane that is defined by the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x plus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y minus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice D is incorrect. This is the center of the circle in the <em>xy</em>-plane that is defined by the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y minus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis x minus 1 right parenthesis squared plus left parenthesis y plus 7 right parenthesis squared equals 1\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>.</p>","externalid":"af30d73b-01f0-4546-bd51-0d5af9b64d57","correct_answer":["C"]}}